{"tid":1648231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣你去左邊到 說好的大遊行","createTime":"2019-10-12T06:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T06:33:07.000Z","uid":121001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cdabdd730b0c2fc3fe16a63cf2853e3c3c33bc07","tid":1648231,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:03:48.000Z","msg":"議會抗爭係民陣同議員代表我地既抗爭手段，有好多籌備工作頭做，大家唔好再話佢地唔搞遊行唔做野住，我暫時留意到佢地現時有既工作<br />\n<br />\n1. 立法會，財委會復會，2019施政報告就黎發報<br />\n2. 區議會選舉<br />\n3. 緊急法司法覆核<br />\n4. 為被捕人士喺法庭上訴訟<br />\n5. 海外宣傳<br />\n等等<br />\n<br />\n我地明白到你地一直都幫我地打緊扙，首先喺度多謝你地先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係依一刻我地真係好需要大遊行，去展示民意，表達訴求同不滿，要話比全球聽，我地仲未輸，仲未放棄<br />\n<br />\n係就係忙左少少，全部和理非想你地再幫我地申請分區合法和平大遊行，應對黨鐵話停就停<br />\n<br />\n提議分三個地方搞，香港九龍新界<br />\n<br />\n推到民陣見到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7407f3068d475d683b0f94a6b933b358e02424d1","tid":1648231,"uid":51368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:07:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"220c79e27e6f52bbd798d1bd8845277ab6588ee9","tid":1648231,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:10:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43a2fa12ab630af15402a6279c09066df9eb14e6","tid":1648231,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c1f46ed5d193386a35d3c85bcb48a3c7d384d80","tid":1648231,"uid":269655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"930d8c26078c09f0cfa937181f06b1f644c4f2d2","tid":1648231,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c62d07a982f750c6ced827318c48338d33782f30","tid":1648231,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:33:07.000Z","msg":"成日搵民陣，佢申請完都要批先得架。"}]}